@startuml
title StockPro - Inter-Service Communication
left to right direction

rectangle Purchase
rectangle Product
rectangle Warehouse
rectangle Movement
rectangle Alert
rectangle Auth
rectangle Report
rectangle Payment
queue Kafka

Purchase --> Product
Purchase --> Warehouse
Warehouse --> Product
Movement --> Product
Movement --> Warehouse
Alert --> Auth
Report --> Product
Report --> Warehouse
Report --> Movement
Report --> Purchase

Purchase --> Kafka : PO created
Kafka --> Payment
Movement --> Kafka : stock events
